.SH CONFIGURATION
.B livs-dwm
is configured by creating a custom
.B config.h
and (re)compiling the source code. This is seen as a feature, not a bug.
.PP
The
.B autostart
patch will execute shell commands from
.I ~/.dwm/autostart.sh
when dwm starts. This is the civilized way to launch your compositor, status bar scripts, and wallpaper daemon.
